    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="myServiceBroker" id="afe50ec7-6f46-4cb0-902d-82c5854d8e2f">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="CM_ServiceBroker"/>
        <text>


This is null for debtors and is only populated for the default.

The default invoice lines are kept on the service broker.</text>
